Writing Task 1
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/TT_GW_008.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Dear Sir/Madam,</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">I am writing to enquire about staying at your hotel as I am planning a trip to Sydney next month.</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">First of all, I would like to know <select id="q1"><option>if it would be</option><option>it would be</option><option>would it be</option><option>if would it be</option></select> possible to book a double room for 7 nights from Friday 16th to Thursday 22nd. Also, we would prefer to stay in a room with a view of Sydney Harbour so could you let me know whether <select id="q2"><option>there are</option><option>there is</option><option>is there</option><option>are there</option></select> any available?</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Secondly, I would be grateful if <select id="q3"><option>you could send</option><option>could you send</option><option>you can send</option><option>you send</option></select> me details of the hotel facilities. I would particularly like to know what outdoor sports facilities <select id="q4"><option>the hotel has</option><option>does the hotel have</option><option>has got the hotel</option><option>has the hotel</option></select>.  For example, <select id="q5"><option>is there</option><option>there is</option><option>there are</option><option>are there</option></select> a swimming pool and <select id="q6"><option>are there</option><option>there is</option><option>is there</option><option>there are</option></select> any tennis courts in the hotel grounds?</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Lastly, I was wondering <select id="q7"><option>if you arrange</option><option>you arrange</option><option>do you arrange</option><option>if do you arrange</option></select> day trips to places in and around Sydney. <select id="q8"><option>Do you have</option><option>You have</option><option>Have you</option><option>You do have</option></select> trips to any of the historical sights or to the mountains, and how much <select id="q9"><option>do they cost</option><option>they cost</option><option>cost they</option><option>they do cost</option></select> ? <select id="q10"><option>Could you</option><option>You can</option><option>You could</option><option>You will</option></select> please send me any brochures you have so that I can plan in advance?</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Thank you for your kind attention. I look forward to hearing from you.</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Yours faithfully,</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Alison Howat</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
